Net-Google-PicasaWeb version 0.01
=================================

Net::Google::PicasaWeb is a set of perl modules providing an Object
Orientated binding to the Google Picasaweb APIs, allowing you to
retrieve information about albums and photos in a picasaweb account,
and to manage (create, delete and upload) albums and photos.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    LWP               (and it's dependencies)
    Crypt::SSLeay     (for https support)
    Scalar::Util      (core since perl 5.8)
    XML::Atom         (and it's dependencies)

Additional modules required for testing (the test suite will skip any
tests that require these modules, and so they do not need to be
installed to use this module):

    Test::More
    Test::Pod           (v1.14 or higher)
    Test::Pos::Coverage (v1.04 or higher)

